public sealed interface RuntimeInvisibleParameterAnnotationsAttribute extends AttributePREVIEW<RuntimeInvisibleParameterAnnotationsAttributePREVIEW>, MethodElementPREVIEW
RuntimeInvisibleParameterAnnotationsAttribute is a preview API of the Java platform.
Programs can only use RuntimeInvisibleParameterAnnotationsAttribute when preview features are enabled.
Preview features may be removed in a future release, or upgraded to permanent features of the Java platform.
Models the RuntimeInvisibleParameterAnnotations attribute 4.7.19, which can appear on methods. Delivered as a MethodElementPREVIEW when traversing a MethodModelPREVIEW.

The attribute does not permit multiple instances in a given location. Subsequent occurrence of the attribute takes precedence during the attributed element build or transformation.

The attribute was introduced in the Java SE Platform version 5.0.
